description: "Map of the Siamese city of Ayutthaya (‘Iudiad’) represented pictorially, surrounded by rivers and with a grid-like layout of roads, rivers and buildings. The city existed from 1350 until 1767 when it was destroyed by an invading Burmese force."
title: "Afbeldinge   der   Stadt   Iudiad   hooft   des   choonincrick   Siam."
